<abstract><t>This document specifies the mapping of defect states between a Pseudo Wire and the Attachment Circuits (AC) of the end-to-end emulated service. This document covers the case whereby the ACs and the PWs are of the same type in accordance to the PWE3 architecture such that a homogenous PW service can be constructed.</t></abstract>

